              <h2>How should readers refine their queries?</h2>
              <ol>
                <li>Add the field of study: "Mercury astronomy" vs "Mercury toxicity".</li>
                <li>Use synonyms where possible: "Quicksilver" for the metal.</li>
                <li>Exclude negative terms: "Mercury -Freddie" if searching for the planet.</li>
